<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error 404 - Recurso no encontrado</title>
    <style>

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-heading {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: black;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 80%;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-heading {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .error-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            img {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <img src="/images/error-404.jpg" alt="Error">
        <h1 class="error-heading">404 - Recurso no encontrado!</h1>
        <p class="error-message">Lo sentimos, el recurso que est√°s buscando no se ha encontrado en el servidor.</p>
        <a href="/" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Regresar</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html> 
